<LegalLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Medical and legal disclaimer for PatientBillGuide educational tools."
  crumbs={[{ label: 'Disclaimer' }]}
>
  <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
  <p>
    Content on PatientBillGuide is for general educational purposes only. It is not medical
    advice, diagnosis, or treatment. For health concerns, contact a licensed clinician.
  </p>

  <h2>Not legal or insurance advice</h2>
  <p>
    We are not attorneys or licensed insurance professionals. Dispute letters and guides are
    editable templates, not legal documents. For legal disputes or plan selection, consult
    qualified professionals.
  </p>

  <h2>No guarantee of savings</h2>
  <p>
    We do not guarantee lower bills, successful disputes, or specific financial outcomes.
    User stories, if published, reflect individual experiences.
  </p>

  <h2>Billing flags are not accusations</h2>
  <p>
    We describe <strong>possible billing concerns</strong> with confidence levels. We do not
    accuse providers of fraud without evidence. A normal result is common and valid.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
  <p>
    Some pages may include disclosed affiliate links in the future. Core tools remain free.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
